  "body": "This issue tracks the overall progress of updating the current beacon chain implementation to spec [v0.2](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/releases/tag/v0.2.0) Here is what has been done so far and the missing steps:\r\n\r\n**Phase 0 Beacon Chain:**\r\n- [ ] introduce \"swap-or-not\" shuffle\r\n- [x] fork choice rule now weighted by balance  #1564\r\n- [x] mix epoch into seed within generate_seed rather than in get_shuffling #1533 \r\n- [x] AttestationData includes latest_crosslink rather than just latest_crosslink_root #1546\r\n- [x] add get_previous_epoch helper #1447 \r\n- [x] add get_total_balance helper \r\n- [x] int_to_bytesN uses little-endian #1536\r\n- [x] minor range fix to verify_bitfield  #1562\r\n- [x] Use 2**63 for GENESIS_SLOT #1537 \r\n\r\n**Phase 0 validator client:**\r\n- [x] implement `get_next_epoch_committee_assignments` #1552\r\n\r\n\r\n**Simple Serialize:**\r\n- [ ] List tree-hash padding consistency fix\r\n- [ ] \"internal\" vs \"external\" hash roots padding fix\r\n\r\n**BLS:**\r\n- [x] rename message -> message_hash in all bls functions #1563 \r\n",
